window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Imani and Isaiah thought they were a match made in heaven. But after a devastating accident leaves Isaiah permanently injured, their new life together starts to fall apart.</p> <p>As Isaiah struggles with depression and doubts, Imani feels their connection drifting away. To make matters worse, their new landlord Jethro engages in increasingly questionable behavior.</p> <p>Things come to a head when tragic truths are revealed, breaking the seemingly unshakable foundation the couple built with one another. But is their marriage the only thing Imani and Isaiah have to worry about? Or is there a much darker, deeper plan in motion? One that could not only end in divorce, but death?</p> <p>A Praying Husband vs A Preying Man is a captivating Christian Romance Thriller full of twists and turns the listeners won't see coming.</p>"; 
